onciliation of the U.S. statutory rate", "bbox": [204.2, 759.1, 1112.4, 779.9]}, {"text": "to its effective income tax rate in Note 15.", "bbox": [162.5, 784.1, 514.5, 804.9]}, {"text": "Because the partnerships have received favorable private letter rulings from the IRS and because the", "bbox": [204.2, 834.1, 1112.4, 854.9]}, {"text": "partnerships’ test procedures conform to IRS guidance, the Corporation’s loss exposure under the synthetic fuel", "bbox": [162.5, 859.1, 1112.4, 879.9]}, {"text": "partnerships is minimal.", "bbox": [162.5, 884.1, 363.6, 904.9]}, {"text": "Note 15.", "bbox": [162.5, 946.4, 235.4, 967.2]}, {"text": "Income Taxes", "bbox": [256.3, 946.4, 379.6, 967.2]}, {"text": "An analysis of the provision for income taxes for income from continuing operations follows:", "bbox": [204.2, 984.1, 986.1, 1004.9]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31", "bbox": [907.3, 1028.7, 1090.2, 1045.4]}, {"text": "2006", "bbox": [900.4, 1053.7, 933.8, 1070.4]}, {"text": "2005", "bbox": [985.5, 1053.7, 1018.9, 1070.4]}, {"text": "2004", "bbox": [1067.2, 1053.7, 1100.5, 1070.4]}, {"text": "(Millions of dollars)", "bbox": [928.5, 1078.7, 1069.0, 1095.4]}, {"text": "Current income taxes:", "bbox": [162.5, 1100.7, 346.7, 1121.6]}, {"text": "United States . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 1125.7, 864.2, 1146.6]}, {"text": "$ 347.8", "bbox": [885.0, 1125.5, 949.3, 1146.4]}, {"text": "$ 308.1", "bbox": [970.1, 1125.7, 1034.4, 1146.6]}, {"text": "$192.0", "bbox": [1055.2, 1125.7, 1112.5, 1146.6]}, {"text": "State . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [204.2, 1150.7, 864.2, 1171.6]}, {"text": "32.8", "bbox": [912.8, 1150.5, 949.3, 1171.4]}, {"text": "66.9", "bbox": [997.9, 1150.7, 1034.4, 1171.6]}, {"text": "35.4", "bbox": [1076.0, 1150.7, 1112.5, 1171.6]}, {"text": "Other countries . . . . . . . . . . 